Release notes
=============

trunk
-------

  * tcsh setup scrtip added
  * improved parameter and localparameter support
  * complex expresions are accepted in the module instantiation 
  * support for compiler directives
  * module slicing added
  * testbench generator added (tbg)
  * grepable list of all wires added by seeg
  * file header added to TMR files (together with revision information)
  * [bug] initial block triplication fixed
  * [bug] tbg does not have to parse the full hierarchy
  
0.1.1
-------

  * minor bug fixes
  * support for ``reg`` and ``wire`` keywords in input/output declaration
  * library names added to configuration file


0.1.0
-------

  * Initial revision


